The files here provide a working, if not complete, latex stylesheet for the NZLSG. This includes a related Lyx style.

At this stage you'll need to understand the configuration of Latex, Lyx and biblatex to use this.

It may be a bit of an arse to setup but once up and running with a Bibtex management systems (e.g. Bibdesk) you'll be rewarded with beautiful output.
  